Pleased to try also:

```
sapply(c("SummarizedExperiment", "MultiAssayExperiment"), library,
character.only = T)
new <- SummarizedExperiment()
metadata(new) <- list(MultiAssayExperiment())
new
```

Again, it is a preference.

kind regards,

Sean

